OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinisters given new        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fguidance on WhatsApp use   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have been given new guidance 
OL,6, on using WhatsApp and other private    
OL,7, messaging apps for government business.
OL,9,FIt replaces previous guidelines from   
OL,10,F2013, before WhatsApp was widely used, 
OL,11,Fon the use of private email.           
OL,13,FThe new guidance states that ministers 
OL,14,Fand officials should use private       
OL,15,Fmessaging apps "with care" and never   
OL,16,Ffor information classified as "secret".
OL,18,FIt follows concerns over the use of    
OL,19,FWhatsApp to discuss key decisions      
OL,20,Fduring the Covid pandemic.             
